description: This premium USB A Male to USB Micro-B Male 5 pin cable features gold plated connectors for corrosion resistance and to ensure consistent and reliable conductivity.The USB 5-Pin Micro-B Cable connects your USB-ready computer or USB hub to a digital camera or other portable device that uses a 5-pin micro-B connector, such as an MP3 player or PDA. This cable is designed and manufactured to USB specifications to ensure it delivers excellent performance under all conditions.Features:* Guaranteed 100% compliance with current USB specifications* Gold plated connectors for corrosion resistance* Molded strain relief construction for flexible movement, durability, and fit* Aluminum undermold contacts reduce crosstalk and interference* 28AWG copper conductors
title: Monoprice 1.5-Feet 28AWG USB 2.0 A Male to 5-pin micro-B Male Cable, Black
